Ludwig - a lattice Boltzmann code for complex fluids

This version of Ludwig has been tested with GCC and Intel MPI.

Quickstart: 
$ cd targetDP
$ make
$ cd ../src
$ make mpi

This will produce an execuatable ./src/Ludwig.exe

* Contact

The original Ludwig is available from

http://ccpforge.cse.rl.ac.uk/gf/project/ludwig/

Please contact l.cebamanos@epcc.ed.ac.uk if you have
any questions or wish to report problems.
